data.description: ***BACK ON THE MARKET***Come see this charming 2 bedroom 2 bathroom home in the heart of Winter Haven! The property is nestled on nearly a quarter acre lot and has a fenced in backyard.  As soon as you walk in the huge cathedral ceilings bring your eyes up and the open floorplan is great for entertaining. Best of all this home has NO HOA and is getting a BRAND NEW ROOF prior to closing.  Other notable upgrades include a BRAND NEW AC unit just installed, ALL NEW PLUMBING throughout, and NO CARPET in the entire home.  Also it is centrally located near LegoLand, shopping, tons of restaurants, schools, town events, and medical facilities.  Plus Highway 27 is just minutes away so it’s just a short commute to I4.  Making the airports, Disney World, Sea World, Universal, and many top Florida beaches all within a short drive!  So call today to set up your private showing before it's too late!
